700053f-a.title: Bronx: 135th Street (East) - St. Ann's Avenue
700053f-a.text:
East 135th Street, east from St. Anns Ave., showing demolition work
in progress on the south side of the street to facilitate the construction
of the approach to the Triborough Bridge.
May 11, 1937.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
